name: CLL
title: LOVE this yogurt
review: I am allergic to all forms of dairy.I have tried many, many diary free yogurts and have have tolerated them at best.... However, when I found this diary free coconut milk yogurt I fell in love!I was very skeptical at first about how it would taste.Surprisingly it tastes and has the texture of a good thick, tart, Greek yogurt.The price is a bit steep but quality products usually are...I purchased the unsweetened plain and it has become my favorite after dinner treat.I mix it with frozen fruit and a bit of grain free, sugar free granola and it makes the perfect yogurt parfait.It is quite a bit more expensive than I like but when you need a good Greek style dairy free yogurt this one is the one I recommend.
